These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, bellflower
1. the person who growsbellflower is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Flower   | bellflower | balloon-flower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: weightlifting, golf
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Sport   | weightlifting | golf |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-3::.
House: victorian, cottage
1. the cottage house is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
2. the cottage house is on the left of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| House   | cottage | victorian |

